      "updated": 1778385497607,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1) Root Node: In a tree data structure, the first node is called as Root Node. Every tree must have root node. ",
      "fontSize": 18.580392485197805,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1) Root Node: In a tree data structure, the first node is called as Root Node. Every tree must have root node. ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "yjd5frPir35jv_noM93m6",
      "type": "text",
