      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1778385708942,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "In a tree data structure, the node which is descendant of any node is called as\nCHILD Node. In",
      "fontSize": 22.30772451059149,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "In a tree data structure, the node which is descendant of any node is called as CHILD Node. In",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "xuzbqpPxHILnArxO3IqZr",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 329.4710435033131,
